      <title>威尔士王妃确诊癌症后首次公开露面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-15/all-eyes-are-on-kate-as-she-returns-to-public-view-at-a-military-parade-honoring-king-charles-iii</link>
